## ğŸ“¡ API Endpoints

### ğŸ”¹ Home

```
GET /
```

Response:

```
Welcome to User API!
```

---

### ğŸ”¹ Add User

```
POST /users
```

JSON Body:

```json
{
  "id": "1",
  "name": "John",
  "age": 22
}
```

---

### ğŸ”¹ Get All Users

```
